stimulusHtml: Which of the following represents the contents of  dataValues  after executing the code segment?

features.html:
Consider the following code segment.

 

ArrayList<Double> dataValues = new ArrayList<Double>();
dataValues.add(9.84);
dataValues.add(8.93);
dataValues.add(7.65);
dataValues.add(6.24);
dataValues.remove(2);
dataValues.set(2, 7.63);
